          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Call this method to initiate the registration process with Apple Push Notification service. If registration succeeds, the app calls your app delegate objectâ€™s  "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiapplicationdelegate/1622958-application"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method and passes it a device token. You should pass this token along to the server you use to generate remote notifications for the device. If registration fails, the app calls its app delegateâ€™s "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiapplicationdelegate/1622962-application"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method instead."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If you want your appâ€™s remote notifications to display alerts, play sounds, or perform other user-facing actions, you must request authorization to do so using the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/usernotifications/unusernotificationcenter/1649527-requestauthorizationwithoptions"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method of "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/usernotifications/unusernotificationcenter"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". If you do not request and receive authorization for your app's interactions, the system delivers all remote notifications to your app silently. "
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
